<title>USA: Bowater sees Q4 gain of about $0.40/shr.</title>
<headline>Bowater sees Q4 gain of about $0.40/shr.</headline>
<dateline>GREENVILLE, S.C. 1996-12-09</dateline>
<text>
<p>Bowater Inc said on Monday that it expects to report an after-tax gain in the fourth quarter of about $17 million or $0.40 per fully diluted share on the previously announced sale of its Star Forms unit.</p>
<p>However, the company said, about half of this gain may be offset by unspecified non-recurring items to be charged to the quarterly operating results.</p>
<p>The company sold the Star Forms unit to CST Office Products Inc for $80 million in November.</p>
